Bus Booking Application
A modern, responsive web application for booking bus tickets built with Python and Flask. This application allows users to search for buses between cities, select their preferred seats, and proceed with booking and payment simulation.

Features
Search Buses: Users can search for available buses between various cities (e.g., Bangalore, Mumbai, Delhi, etc.) on specific dates.
Dynamic Seat Selection: Interactive seat layout with randomized pre-booked seat generation (for demonstration).
Booking Flow: Users can select seats and generate a booking summary.
Payment Simulation: A mock payment gateway that confirms the booking and generates a unique Booking ID.
Session Management: Temporary storage of booking details using Flask sessions.
Tech Stack
Backend: Python, Flask
Frontend: HTML5, CSS3, Jinja2 Templates
Data Storage: In-memory Python data structures (Lists & Dictionaries) for storing Bus and Seat data
